{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-ST-3", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "請君入甕", "storyInfo": "游輪的客房中，陳找到埃內斯托，埃內斯托承認自己是主謀，陳卻指出他在說謊。\n被揭穿的埃內斯托表示陳來晚了。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G06"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸，下面的人讓我告訴你，準備都做好啦。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#7"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？爸爸，你好像不怎麼高興？", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#2"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#2"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？爸爸不是等這一天等了很久嗎？", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#2"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉是個難纏的女人，不到最後一刻都不能放鬆警惕。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#5"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉菲艾拉。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#2"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果情況不對，你就讓埃內斯托那小子帶你跑。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誒？我要和爸爸在一起。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#2"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別任性。本來，這件事就不該把你捲進來的。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老皮尤要是知道他託付給我的女兒跟著我幹這個，怕是要從墳墓裡爬起來宰了我。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#2"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於埃內斯托那小子......哼。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#2"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哥哥怎麼啦？", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那小子以為我看不出來，他那點心思，我怎麼可能看不出來。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#2"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哥哥沒有背叛哦。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，沒有這小子，這事成不了。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他其實不想這麼做。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是為什麼呢？", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#2"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰不想吃好喝好睡好，不去想那些有的沒的？", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潘喬揉了揉站在身邊的養女的頭。"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，乖，去把我的煙斗拿來，我要一個人靜一靜。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#2"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦......", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#6"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#2", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳小姐，你來了。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "林小姐呢，我以為她會和你一起。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你不打算掩飾了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkalley_intro", "key": "$darkalley_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#6", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老實說，都到了這份上，我也沒有什麼掩飾的必要了，不是嗎？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我確實沒有想到，你們居然這樣都能突破出來。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是小看了你們。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我很好奇，你們是怎麼發現的？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "林雨霞在第一輪就發現了你們在安裝炸藥，只是我們沒有告訴你。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......在那時候，我就被懷疑了？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個時候只是以防萬一罷了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們確認你有問題，是因為在你的武器店裡發現了同樣的炸藥。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#4", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來如此。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到勝負在這麼早就分出來了。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#4", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在是什麼意思，垂死掙扎？還是想要自首？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是有一些話想說，陳小姐。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽完或許你會有不同的看法。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洗耳恭聽。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳小姐，你知道玻利瓦爾的歷史嗎？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不怎麼清楚。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#6", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是，你過去是在維多利亞留學，維多利亞沒有怎麼插手玻利瓦爾的事，想來不特意調查的話不會知道得很清楚。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在伊比利亞發現這片土地之前，這裡只是一片叫做玻利瓦爾的平原。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊比利亞人在這裡發現了許多源石礦脈，於是他們駐足於此，將這裡變成了他們的附屬地。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，因為種種原因，伊比利亞的統治終結了。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經過混亂的一百三十年後，萊塔尼亞人來了。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是玻利瓦爾又成為了萊塔尼亞的附屬地。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩百年前，玻利瓦爾從附屬地演變成了附屬國，也就是辛嘉斯王朝。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以說，玻利瓦爾是從那個時候才成為了現在的玻利瓦爾——雖然辛嘉斯王朝的人從不自稱玻利瓦爾人。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，巫王時期，萊塔尼亞試圖透過玻利瓦爾在哥倫比亞掀起內亂。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，這麼做的結果卻是，內亂不僅失敗，玻利瓦爾反被哥倫比亞入侵，聯合政府就是在那時候建立的。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玻利瓦爾從此進入了哥倫比亞和萊塔尼亞割據的狀態。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊塔尼亞對於玻利瓦爾並沒有那麼在意，而哥倫比亞雖然野心勃勃卻也沒有辦法一口吞下。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雙方於是進入了拉鋸狀態。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而後，再也無法忍受這種狀態的玻利瓦爾人選擇了反抗。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們成立了反抗軍，自稱真正玻利瓦爾人，並立誓將玻利瓦爾變成真正獨立的國家。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，事情並沒有好轉，真正玻利瓦爾人的建立只是將玻利瓦爾拖入更深的泥潭。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，玻利瓦爾變成了現在這副樣子。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聯合政府，辛嘉斯王朝，真正玻利瓦爾人，三方陷入了永無止境的戰火之中。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不僅如此，在這樣的環境中，誕生了多索雷斯這樣一座城市。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在坎黛拉女士的治理下，這座城市不僅在三方政府中都吃得開，而且甚至很多時候三方都要賣坎黛拉女士人情。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為這座城市坐擁他們無法忽視的資源，而且坎黛拉女士手上也有足夠的力量保護這座城市。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座城市於是逐漸成為了玻利瓦爾人人都嚮往的地方。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一個飽受戰火折磨的玻利瓦爾人，心中的夢想都是存錢來這裡玩，甚至是在這裡翻身。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#4", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，像你和林小姐這樣的好人一定是明白的，陳小姐。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座城市是一個怎樣的地方。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#2", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果說三方政府至少還有統一玻利瓦爾的心思，那坎黛拉女士則毫無這方面的想法。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說白了吧，陳小姐，這座城市的繁榮建立在整個玻利瓦爾的痛苦之上。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它越繁榮，這個國家就越沒有希望。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是許多真正熱愛玻利瓦爾這片土地的人無法接受的事。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也是其中一員？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這座城市不應該存在於玻利瓦爾這樣的地方。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的目的是毀掉這座城市。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#2", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，毀掉的話，太浪費了。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的目的是製造恐慌。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你說這些是想說服我幫助你們？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不敢，用幾句話就說服別人加入自己，我還沒那麼有自信。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我希望你和林小姐能夠至少袖手旁觀。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們應該能夠發現，我們的事業堪稱正義，陳小姐。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要兩位不出手，我保證我的人不會對兩位出手。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位很強大，這一點，跟著兩位一路參加比賽的我感受最為深刻。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和兩位起衝突的話，會帶來許多不必要的損失。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望你和林小姐能夠考慮這個提案。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃內斯托。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請說。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在不久以前，經歷過一場比這一次要複雜得多的陰謀，在那場陰謀中，我除了認清了自己的弱小，沒有獲得任何東西。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我至少還是敢這麼斷言——沒有一種給他人帶去恐懼的東西，可以自稱正義。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#2", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#2", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，你沒有說實話。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不懂你在說什麼，陳小姐，我已經承認了我是這次的主謀。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，你不是。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我起疑的是你將我們困在你的武器店這個行為。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這雖然相當有效，但也相當勉強，我認為你不會不去考慮暴露自己身份的可能性。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我開始思考，你會不會還有後手。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果你是這一切的幕後主使，如果你的身份暴露，那我想不到有什麼後手可以補救這一點。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後我想到了，如果你的身份並不那麼重要，也就是說，其實你暴露了也無所謂。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是這樣，那就說得通了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對你來說，能夠困住我們最好，但如果困不住而且暴露了，那也不過是變成現在這樣的局面。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我站在你的面前，將你當做這一切的主使，而無法看清你背後的東西。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到現在，我也依然身在你的局中，是這樣吧，埃內斯托。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#6", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真正身在局中的人，是不會說出這樣的話的，陳小姐。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#6", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是我們掌握的情報太少，以至於即使我知道這是一個局，我也必須跳進去。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#6", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，僅憑著少得可憐的線索，就能在這短短一周裡差一點抓到我們精心策劃幾年的計畫核心。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳小姐，你和林小姐還是太厲害了。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#6", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的，有許多人說我太小題大做，將兩位當成了自己的主要對手。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但從我的角度來說，我很慶幸我這麼做了，否則，要是我疏忽一點，多洩露一些東西，兩位就已經發現了。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜，兩位還是失敗了。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃內斯托說著，打開了電視。"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}